{"created": "2026-03-17T07:57:55.875898", "current_version": "1.0.0", "project": "ESP32 Distance Sensor", "versions": {"1.0.0": {"created": "2026-03-17T07:57:55.875896", "creator": {"program": "sphinx_needs", "version": "7.0.0"}, "needs": {"API_COMP_NETIF_TUNNEL": {"acceptance_criteria": "", "api_signature": "", "arch": {}, "avatar": null, "closed_at": null, "completion": null, "component": "", "constraints": [], "constraints_error": null, "constraints_passed": true, "constraints_results": {}, "content": "**Brief Description**\n\nUART-based IP tunnel network interface for QEMU simulator. Provides a lwIP network interface that tunnels IP packets over UART1, enabling full TCP/IP stack functionality in QEMU without network device emulation.\n\nKey features:\n\n* QEMU UART network bridge for ESP32 emulation\n* lwIP network interface over UART1\n* Simple length-prefixed framing protocol\n* Conditional compilation for QEMU only\n\n**Architecture:**\n\n- ESP32 (QEMU): lwIP stack -> netif -> UART1 -> TCP socket\n- Host: TCP socket -> TUN device -> Linux network stack", "created_at": null, "docname": "21_api/api_netif_uart_tunnel", "doctype": ".rst", "duration": null, "external_css": "external_link", "external_url": null, "has_dead_links": false, "has_forbidden_dead_links": false, "header_file": "main/components/netif_uart_tunnel/netif_uart_tunnel_sim.h", "id": "API_COMP_NETIF_TUNNEL", "id_prefix": null, "is_external": false, "is_import": false, "is_modified": false, "jinja_content": false, "layout": null, "lineno": 4, "links": ["REQ_NETIF_TUNNEL_1", "REQ_NETIF_TUNNEL_2", "REQ_NETIF_TUNNEL_5"], "links_back": [], "max_amount": null, "max_content_lines": null, "modifications": 0, "parameters": "", "params": null, "parent_need": null, "parent_needs": [], "parent_needs_back": [], "parts": {}, "post_content": null, "post_template": null, "pre_content": null, "pre_template": null, "prefix": null, "priority": "", "query": null, "rationale": "", "returns": "", "section_name": "Netwo